com.facebook.litho

Class DisabledMountContentPool

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.facebook.litho.DisabledMountContentPool
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    MountContentPool, PoolWithDebugInfo

    public class DisabledMountContentPool
extends Object
implements MountContentPool
    A MountContentPool that has no size and doesn't recycle objects. Return from OnCreateMountContentPool to disable recycling.

                      ComponentLifecycle lifecycle)
        Description copied from interface: MountContentPool
        Return a recycled mount content, or a newly acquired mount content if there isn't one to recycle. Should not return null.

        NB: This can be called from multiple threads, possibly at the same time!

      • maybePreallocateContent

        public void maybePreallocateContent(Context c,
                                    ComponentLifecycle lifecycle)
        Description copied from interface: MountContentPool
        Called when a LayoutState that uses this mount content type may be used in the near future. The pool is given a chance to create mount content and put it in the pool in anticipation of a acquire call.

        NB: This can be called from multiple threads, possibly at the same time!

        Specified by:
        maybePreallocateContent in interface MountContentPool
